OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMetro Bank scraps seven-day
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fa week opening             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Metro Bank is to end seven-day trading 
OL,6, in all its branches and cut about 1,000
OL,7, jobs after reporting huge losses.      
OL,9,FFrom 29 March, all 76 branches will    
OL,10,Fclose on Sundays and Bank Holidays,    
OL,11,Fwith more than half of them closing on 
OL,12,FSaturdays as well.                     
OL,14,FThe lender also said it would cut 22%  
OL,15,Fof its workforce by mid-April as part  
OL,16,Fof a huge cost-cutting exercise.       
OL,18,FThe struggling High Street bank began a
OL,19,Freview of operations last autumn in an 
OL,20,Feffort to save about #50m a year.      
